le=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/20118281015368738055.jpg\" border=\"0\" />\n</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>           你大爷的，外加你大姨妈的，自己家真的富呀？</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>                     </strong></p>\n<p><strong>   <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" height=\"427\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/2011828102354994754.jpg\" width=\"600\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>                     <br />\n很特色的建筑！</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>           <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/20118281033363846255.jpg\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>       知道你丈夫为什么会唤醒么？因为有个人正要成为另类植物人。</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\n<p><strong>       先说说我们的股市。。。。。。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>                  </strong></p>\n<p><strong>                  <br />\n <img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/20118281054463349124.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>                             <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/20118281057356233310.gif\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>                       </strong><strong>             <span><img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/29/2011829137368779254.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></span>  </strong></p>\n<p><span> <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/20118281108623828.gif\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>                  <br />\n <br />\n当今的中国，老太太扶不起，A股炒不起</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>            <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/2011828125352511828.jpg\" name=\"image_operate_56161315194892272\" /><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>                     <br />\n 同是七月二十三</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>           <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/2011828165264571490.jpg\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p><strong>              </strong></p>\n<p><strong>               说的没错，是差距！但出现差距的根源在哪呢。。。。。。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>                       </strong></p>\n<p><strong>       <br />\n  <img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/20118282023557064837.jpg\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p><strong>    两岸统一的不仅仅只是疆域，更重要的是治国的理念！（直言语）</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>                  </strong><br />\n<span><strong><img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/2011828944104371402.jpg\" name=\"image_operate_74121315196003493\" /><br />\n  </strong></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>                  <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/2011828947142364749.jpg\" /><br />\n<br /></strong></span><br />\n                   <strong>差距以表相的形态出现，它不是装出来的！<br /></strong></p>\n<p><strong>                      </strong></p>\n<p><strong>             <br />\n  <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/08/28/20118282053224910144.gif\" border=\"0\" /><br />\n<br />\n                <br />\n <br />\n猫与哪个部门最像？<br /></strong></p>\n<p><strong>                    </strong></p>\n<p><strong>      <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.