rong>今年开征月饼税！天才呀，大姨妈呀！</strong></div>\n<div> </div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>\n                    <span><img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/09/02/20119212868180636.jpg\" border=\"0\" name=\"image_operate_63391315194978502\" /></span></div>\n<div>\n          <br />\n<strong>“套套”真的是个好东东，白天套啼子，晚上套根子</strong></div>\n<div> </div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>\n          <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/09/02/2011921536225859775.jpg\" border=\"0\" name=\"image_operate_85691315194797232\" />\n</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>\n          <strong> <br />\n从小就受到教育，要有一颗感恩的心。</strong></div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>\n                     </div>\n<div>\n        <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/09/02/2011921629378323047.jpg\" border=\"0\" name=\"image_operate_97571315194799372\" />\n</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>\n                      </div>\n<div>\n       <img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/09/01/2011911944576243472.JPG\" /></p>\n<p>      <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/09/01/2011911945191669726.JPG\" /><br />\n<br />\n      <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/09/01/201191194551543078.JPG\" /><br />\n</div>\n<div>\n      <br />\n<img title=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" alt=\"[转载]笑中有泪，乐中有哀！鈥斺斺斖妓堤煜\" src=\"http://upfile1cdn.kdnet.net/UploadSmall/2011/09/01/2011911946191876132.JPG\" name=\"image_operate_64301315194828100\" />\n</div>\n<div><span><span><strong>善于下跪的民族：</strong></span></span></div>\n<div><span><span><strong>   当你的思想只有“他”的时候，其悲惨命运已经注定！！！</strong></span></span></div>\n<div><strong>                                          